## 9. [Templates](#9-templates)
- Purpose: Templates are special objects which define a Gravwell query containing variables.
- [Documentation](https://docs.gravwell.io/gui/templates/templates.html)
- Total: 15
- ***General Disclaimer*** for all Templates
    - Fortinet EV 0 must be populated with a variable.
    - Fortinet EV 1 & Fortinet EV 2 may be left empty.
- Template - Fortinet - Events - EV - Count [table]
    - Displays a table of the specified Fortinet Events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs). Used on the Fortinet Events Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - Events - EV - Count [chart]
    - Displays a chart of the specified Fortinet Events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs). Used on the Fortinet Events Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - Events - EV - Count [numbercard]
    - Displays a numbercard of the specified Fortinet Events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs). Used on the Fortinet Events Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - Traffic - EV - Count [chart]
    - Displays a chart of the specified Fortinet Traffic events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs). Used on the Fortinet Traffic Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - Traffic - EV - Count [table]
    - Displays a table of the specified Fortinet Traffic events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs). Used on the Fortinet Traffic Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - Traffic - EV - Count [numbercard]
    - Displays a numbercard of the specified Fortinet Traffic events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs). Used on the Fortinet Traffic Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - UTM - EV - Count [table]
    - Displays a table of the specified Fortinet UTM events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs). Used on the Fortinet UTM Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - UTM - EV - Count [numbercard]
    - Displays a numbercard of the specified Fortinet UTM events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs). Used on the Fortinet UTM Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - UTM - EV - Count [chart]
    - Displays a chart of the specified Fortinet UTM events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs). Used on the Fortinet UTM Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - System - EV - Count [chart]
    - Displays a chart of the specified Fortinet System events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs). Used on the Fortinet System Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - System - EV - Count [table]
    - Displays a table of the specified Fortinet System events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs). Used on the Fortinet System Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - System - EV - Count [numbercard]
    - Displays a numbercard of the specified Fortinet System events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs). Used on the Fortinet System Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - General - EV - Count [chart]
    - Displays a chart of Fortinet events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs) across all Fortinet log types. Used on the General Fortinet Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - General - EV - Count [numbercard]
    - Displays a numbercard of Fortinet events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs) across all Fortinet log types. Used on the General Fortinet Overview dashboard.
- Template - Fortinet - General - EV - Count [table]
    - Displays a table of Fortinet events grouped by the specified Enumerated Values (EVs) across all Fortinet log types. Used on the General Fortinet Overview dashboard.

